Package edu.asu.cse360.team9

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    This class is supposed to provide a common pass-through between the GUI layer and the internal model.
    Graph
    Provides representation of a directed graph as an adjacency list.
    MainFrame
    Main frame of application, which provides user ability to enter a collection of activities by rows along with their dependencies and durations.
    Paths
    Displays the results of successful calculation as a table of paths and their durations ordered by duration descending.
    Record
    Represents a non-GUI tied model object of Activity, Duration, Path.
    Result
    Represents a non-GUI model object of Path, Total Duration
